data.description: Who says there are no good deals anymore? Whether you are a First-Time-buyer or a seasoned Investor; THIS IS your opportunity! Presenting this MASSIVE Two Family House (with 2 additional units) on 80 Scribner avenue; 2 Bedrooms on the 1st FL, 3 bedrooms on the 2nd FL, 1 Bedroom in the Attic (Attic also has a separate entrance believe it or not) and 3 Bedrooms in the basement. This Home has been well taken care of and Maintained for years, just waiting for the next occupant to put their own cosmetic touch to it. Say it with me; CONVENIENCE, right by Clove Lake Park, less than a 10 minute walk to the Ferry, experience the tranquility of the Suburban feel while also being minuted away from shops, parks, highways & pubic transportation. Brand New Solar Panels for efficiency. Plenty of Street Parking. Home will be delivered vacant. Large 30 X 100 Lot, the possibilities are endless, Call to Schedule a showing today!
